{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"automation"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Braze\/documentation\/BrazeKit\/Braze\/Configuration-swift.class\/Push-swift.class\/Automation-swift.class","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Automation","preciseIdentifier":"s:8BrazeKit0A0C13ConfigurationC4PushC10AutomationC"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"style":"important","name":"Important","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK must be initialized on the main thread to enable push notification"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"automation. SDK initialization must happen before the application has finished launching","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or in your AppDelegate ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/archive.is\/nUG1k","type":"reference"},{"text":" implementation.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If the application setup requires the SDK to be initialized after the application has"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"finished launching, refer to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Braze\/documentation\/BrazeKit\/Braze\/prepareForDelayedInitialization(pushAutomation:analyticsBehavior:)"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The automation steps performed by the SDK are compatible with pre-existing push"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"notification handling integrations in your codebase. The SDK only automates the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"processing of remote notification received from Braze. Any system handler implemented","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to process your own or another third party SDK remote notifications will continue to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"work when "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automation"},{"type":"text","text":" is enabled."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the SDK does not perform any automation steps and you are required to implement"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIApplicationDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" methods yourself as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"described in the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Braze\/tutorials\/Braze\/b1-standard-push-notifications"},{"text":" tutorial.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can enable automatic push notification handling as follows:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":null,"code":["configuration.push.automation = true"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This instructs the SDK to:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register your application for push notification on the system."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Request the push notification authorization \/ permission at initialization.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Dynamically provide implementations for the push notification related system delegate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"methods.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For a more granular behavior, each automation step can be enabled individually:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Automate only the `application(_:didRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithDeviceToken:)`","\/\/ delegate method","configuration.push.automation.registerDeviceToken = true"],"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Or you can perform a combination of both approaches:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["\/\/ Enable all automations","configuration.push.automation = true","\/\/ Disable the automatic notification authorization request at launch.","configuration.push.automation.requestAuthorizationAtLaunch = false"],"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"aside","style":"important","name":"Important","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When enabled, the ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIApplicationDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" methods will not be executed when processing remote"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"notifications received from Braze.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Braze\/documentation\/BrazeKit\/Braze\/Notifications-swift.class\/subscribeToUpdates(payloadTypes:_:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to subscribe to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"those push notification updates when ","type":"text"},{"code":"automation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is enabled."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The behavior of each automation step is described in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Braze\/documentation\/BrazeKit\/Braze\/Configuration-swift.class\/Push-swift.class\/Automation-swift.class","type":"refe